  "name": "RPlog_You_Wouldn_t_Like_Me_When_I_m_Angry",
  "title": "Too Late to Save Her",
  "summary": "Hearing a woman's scream in a slum alley, the philanthropic Quarren Thrask rushes in only to watch the bounty hunter Danik snatch up the crippled Kyokusha and fly off toward his ship, the Vendetta, leaving two henchmen behind to delay any pursuit. Enraged, Thrask charges the armored Sethas and the sniper Sandor, drawing blaster and sword. A brutal close-quarters brawl erupts: Sandor's rifle shot nearly takes Thrask's leg, Sethas tries to grapple the squid's sword arm and is caught by friendly fire, and Thrask's blind rage carries him through wound after wound until he runs Sethas through, dropping him bleeding in the sand. Meanwhile Danik secures Kyokusha in stun cuffs aboard the Vendetta and returns overhead, using his ship's tractor beam to hurl debris at Thrask. A crate slams into the raging Quarren and throws him from his feet, leaving him beaten in the alley with the bitter knowledge that he has failed to save her.",
